<h3 class="tool_heading">Mental Health Resources</h3>
<p dir="ltr">Taking good care of yourself and your family during these uncertain times is critical. In the case of a mental health emergency, please contact Northwest Connections by dialing 211.</p>
<p dir="ltr">In addition to this, here are some other very helpful resources to use in a mental health crisis situation:</p>
<ul>
<li dir="ltr">
<p dir="ltr">Northwest Connections Mental Health Crisis Line: 1-888-552-6642</p>
</li>
<li dir="ltr">
<p dir="ltr">National Suicide Prevention Lifeline: 1-800-273-TALK</p>
</li>
<li dir="ltr">
<p dir="ltr">Crisis Text Line - Text HOPELINE to 741741</p>
</li>
</ul>
